@baseUrl=http://localhost:9005

### greeting and name
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Hi, my name is Bob!",
  "conversationId": "test-conversation-01"
}

### ask back the name
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Do you know my name?",
  "conversationId": "test-conversation-01"
}
